<td background="/lotr/gfx/mom/blu_05.gif" class="headerbg"><font class="h1font"><font color="#FFFFFF">Fun Decks</font></B></td><td background="/lotr/gfx/mom/blu_06.gif"></td></tr>
	<tr><td background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_07.gif"></td>
		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Han Frodo</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.73)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=21632">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=9608">Andy "acw10016" Wong</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=9608&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> This deck monopolizes on cardinal principle #4, twilight control, which I discussed in my strategy article, &quot;The 3 cardinal principles of card gaming&quot;.

I first got the idea for this deck when playing a game in which I lost all my starters exc</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> February 21, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> The Good (34)<br>
Starting Fellowship:<br>
Han Frodo- Old Bilbo&#39;s Heir<br>
The Ruling Ring<br>
<br>
Companions:<br>
Boromir U x2<br>
Aragorn R<br>
<br>
Possessions:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(194)">Sting</a> x 2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(198)">Thror&#39;s Map</a> x 2<br>
<br>
Allies:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(170)">Bounder</a> x 4<br>
Bilbo x 2<br>
Gaffer x 2<br>
Party Guest x 2<br>
Thrarin<br>
<br>
Events Gondor:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(883)">Elendil&#39;s Valor</a><br>
<br>
Events Shire:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(179)">Hobbit Stealth</a> x 4<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(178)">Hobbit Intuition</a> x 4<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(171)">Extraordinary Resilience</a> x 2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(872)">Halfling Deftness</a> x 3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(190)">Power According to His Stature</a> x 2<br>
<br>
Axis of Evil (34)<br>
Nazgul:<br>
Ulaire Enquea x 2<br>
Ulaire Nertea x 2<br>
<br>
